// Modal.js import React from 'react'; import Table from 'react-bootstrap/Table'; const Modal = ({ isOpen, onClose, event }) => { // Null check for event if (!event) { return null; // Return null if event is null } // Null check for start and end properties const start = event.start ? event.start.toLocaleString() : 'N/A'; const end = event.end ? event.end.toLocaleString() : 'N/A'; return (
{event.title}
# start Last Name Username
{start} Mark Otto @mdo
2 Jacob Thornton @fat
3 Larry the Bird @twitter

Start: {start}

End: {end}

Description: {event.description}

); }; export default Modal;
